snippet.title: Timelie - Official Trailer - Available now on PC
snippet.description:
Get Timelie on your Steam now:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1150950/Timelie/

A mysterious girl able to envision the past and the future, trapped in a world where time flows and ebbs in strange and unpredictable ways. A cat, seemingly connected to the world, becomes her sole ally. Their connection spans time and space, and only through teamwork can they unravel the secrets behind where they are...and why.

Only through teamwork can the girl and the cat find a way to escape. But, they have time.

Timelie is available now on PC on May 21, 2020
For more information on Timelie, please visit: http://timeliegame.com
- Timelie Facebook fanpage: https://www.facebook.com/TimelieGame/
- Urnique Studio Twitter: https://twitter.com/UrniqueStudio
- Urnique Studio fanpage: https://www.facebook.com/urniquestudio/
